  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Thermal Protection System</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Significantly improves survival times in <span class=\"name name-fuel\">high-temperature environments</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装热能防护系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>显著提升<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高温环境</span>中的生存时间。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装热能防护系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>显著地提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">高温环境</span>中的生存时间。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝熱能防護系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">重大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>顯著提升<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高溫環境</span>生存時間。"
